    "use strict";

this.author = "Spara";
this.name = "SIRF_market";

this.$originalDefs = 
{
    "food": [ 0, 0, 35, -2, 2, 40, 1, 4, 0 ],
    "textiles": [ 0, 0, 25, -2, 3, 20, 2, 3, 0 ],
    "radioactives": [ 0, 0, 75, -3, 4, 22, 2, 4, 0 ],
    "slaves": [ 0, 0, 55, 5, -2, 5, 1, 1, 0 ],
    "liquor_wines": [ 0, 0, 90, -4, 4, 15, 2, 3, 0 ],
    "luxuries": [ 0, 0, 250, -4, 2, 5, 2, 2, 0 ],
    "narcotics": [ 0, 0, 0, 0, -1, -3, 1, 0, 0 ],
    "computers": [ 0, 0, 172, -3, 4, 42, 1, 2, 0 ],
    "machinery": [ 0, 0, 146, -3, 3, 45, 4, 4, 0 ],
    "alloys": [ 0, 0, 85, -2, 3, 30, 2, 2, 0 ],
    "firearms": [ 0, 0, 140, -1, 3, 0, 1, 3, 0 ],
    "furs": [ 0, 0, 175, 3, -2, 6, 1, 3, 0 ],
    "minerals": [ 0, 0, 40, -1, 2, 35, 4, 4, 0 ],
    "gold": [ 0, 0, 83, -2, 3, 20, 3, 4, 1 ],
    "platinum": [ 0, 0, 152, -2, 2, 24, 3, 3, 1 ],
    "gem_stones": [ 0, 0, 42, -1, 3, 25, 2, 2, 2 ],
    "alien_items": [ 0, 0, 98, -4, 4, 12, 5, 5, 0 ]
};

this.updateLocalCommodityDefinition = function(goodDefinition) 
{
    var commodity = goodDefinition.key;
    var oldDefs = this.$originalDefs[commodity];
    
    //define the market size for the station
    goodDefinition.capacity = 127;

    //old style definition found for the good. calculate it the old way
    if (oldDefs) 
    {
        var market_base_price = oldDefs[2];
        var market_eco_adjust_price = oldDefs[3];
        var market_eco_adjust_quantity = oldDefs[4];
        var market_base_quantity = oldDefs[5];
        var market_mask_price = oldDefs[6];
        var market_mask_quantity = oldDefs[7];
        var market_rnd = Math.floor(Math.random() * 256);

        var economy = system.economy;
        
        var price = (market_base_price + (market_rnd & market_mask_price) + (economy * market_eco_adjust_price)) & 255;
        price *= 0.4;
        
        var quantity = (market_base_quantity + (market_rnd & market_mask_quantity) - (economy * market_eco_adjust_quantity)) & 255;
        if (quantity > 127) quantity = 0;
        
        quantity &= 63;
        
        goodDefinition.quantity = quantity;
        goodDefinition.price = price * 10;
    }


    //no definition found. just add some variance to the system market (+/-5%)
    else 
    {
        goodDefinition.price = goodDefinition.price * (1.05 - Math.random() * 0.1);
        goodDefinition.quantity = Math.floor(goodDefinition.quantity * (1.05 - Math.random() * 0.1));
    }

    //no definition found. no market on that commodity
    //else {
    //    goodDefinition.price = 0;
    //    goodDefinition.quantity = 0;
    //    goodDefinition.capacity = 0;
    //}

    //scale down if quantity too high
    if (goodDefinition.quantity > goodDefinition.capacity)
        goodDefinition.quantity = Math.floor(goodDefinition.quantity / 127 * goodDefinition.capacity);

    return goodDefinition;
};
    Scripts/SIRF_populator.js 
    this.name           = "SIRF_populator";
this.author         = "Dybal, based on the concept of Tinker";
this.description    = "Script to add SIRF stations to certain systems";
this.version        = "2.62";
this.copyright      = "Creative Commons: attribution, non-commercial, sharealike";
this.licence   		= "CC BY-NC-SA 4.0";
"use strict";

this.systemWillPopulate = function () 
{
    if (system.isInterstellarSpace || system.sun.isGoingNova || system.sun.hasGoneNova || 
        system.government < 3 || system.techLevel < 7 || system.techLevel > 13 || 
        system.countShipsWithRole("SIRF-YARD") > 0)
        return;

    var pos = system.mainPlanet.position.multiply(-1.5);

    system.setPopulator("SIRF", {
        callback: function(pos) {
                let a = system.addShips("SIRF-YARD", 1, pos, 0)[0];
                var i = Math.max((a.entityPersonality&7),1),p;
                while (i--) {
                    p = Vector3D.random(22000);
                    if (i>>1) system.addShips("trader", 1, a.position.add(p), 500);
                    if ((i&2)>>1) system.addShips("pirate", 1, a.position.add(p), 500);
                    if ((i&1)===1) system.addShips("police", 1, a.position.add(p), 500);
                }
            }.bind(this),
        location: "COORDINATES",
        coordinates: pos,
        deterministic: true
    });
}
    Scripts/SIRF_ship_script.js 
    this.name			= "SIRF_ship_script";
this.author			= "Montana05";
this.description	= "ship script for SIRF.OXP";
this.version		= "2.62";
this.copyright		= "2021 Montana05";
this.licence   		= "CC BY-NC-SA 4.0";
"use strict";

this.shipSpawned = function(ship)
{
	this.$SIRF_shipType = this.ship.dataKey;
	this.$SIRF_shipRole = this.ship.primaryRole;

	var dice = 0;

	if(this.ship.hasRole("escape-capsule"))
	{
		// neutral inits first
		var crewName = expandDescription("[nom]");
		var crewDescription = "a crew member of an evacuated ship";
		var crewRole = "hunter";  // not perfect but somewhere in the middle
		var crewRace = expandDescription("[MRP01_GalCop_races_scientific]");  // add a race to the crew members
		
		this.$SIRF_crewRanks_fighter_array = ["Gunner", "Co-Pilot", "Pilot", "Commander"];
		var crewRanks_fighter = 
		$SIRF_crewRanks_fighter_array[Math.floor(Math.random() * $SIRF_crewRanks_fighter_array.length)];

		this.$SIRF_stationRanks_array = ["an employee", "a resident", "a visitor"];
		var stationRanks = 
		$SIRF_stationRanks_array[Math.floor(Math.random() * $SIRF_stationRanks_array.length)];

		switch(this.$SIRF_shipType) 
		{
			case "SIRF_worm_prospector_lifeboat":

				dice = this.$getRndInteger(1, 5);

				if(dice == 5)
				{	
					crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " Pilot " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
					crewDescription = "a SIRF ship crew member";
					crewRole = "trader";
				}
				else
				{	
					crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
					crewDescription = (stationRanks + " " + "of a SIRF station");
					crewRole = "passenger";
				};	
				
				this.ship.switchAI("homeAI.plist");
				break;
			
			case "SIRF_escape_pod_SIRF":
				
				crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
				crewDescription = (stationRanks + " " + "of a SIRF station");
				crewRole = "passenger";
				break;
						
			case "SIRF_escape_capsule_SIRF":

				dice = this.$getRndInteger(1, 5);

				if(dice == 5)
				{	
					crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " Pilot " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
					crewDescription = "a SIRF ship crew member";
					crewRole = "trader";
				}
				else
				{	
					crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
					crewDescription = "a traveller on a SIRF ship";
					crewRole = "passenger";
				};	
				break;

			case "SIRF_escape_suit_SIRF":
			
				crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " Specialist " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
				crewDescription = "a prospector of a SIRF station";
				crewRole = "miner";
				break;
				
			case "SIRF_escape_capsule_ssg":	
		
				crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " " + crewRanks_fighter + " " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
				crewDescription = "a SSG ship crew member";
				crewRole = "hunter";
				break;
			
			case "SIRF_escape_capsule_neutral":
			case "SIRF_escape_suit_neutral":	
							
				if(this.$SIRF_shipType == "SIRF_escape_suit_neutral")
					dice = 5;
				else
				{	
					dice = this.$getRndInteger(1, 5);
				};	

				if(dice == 5)
				{	
					crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " Pilot " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
					crewDescription = "a ship crew member";
					crewRole = "trader";
				}
				else
				{	
					crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " " + expandDescription("[nom]"));
					crewDescription = "a interplanetar passenger";
					crewRole = "passenger";
				};
				break;	

			case "SIRF_escape_capsule_SIRF_pirate":
			case "SIRF_escape_suit_SIRF_pirate":
			case "SIRF_escape_suit_pirate":
			case "SIRF_escape_capsule_pirate":
			case "SIRF_escape_capsule_ssg_pirate":			
		
				crewName = ("the " + crewRace + " " + expandDescription("[MRP01_pirate_nicknames]") + expandDescription("[nom]"));
				crewDescription = "a criminal wanted by GalCop police";
				crewRole = "pirate";
				break;	
				
			default: 
				break;		
		};

		this.ship.setCrew
		(
			{
				name: crewName,
				short_description: crewDescription,
				role: crewRole,
				species: crewRace
			}
		);

		// remove individual roles
		this.ship.primaryRole = "escape-capsule";
	}
	else
	{
		switch(this.$SIRF_shipType) 
		{
			case "SIRF_shuttle_system":
			case "SIRF_shuttle_system_team_01":	
		
				if(this.ship.cargoSpaceUsed <= 15)
				{
					var coinFlip = this.$getRndInteger(1, 2);
				
					if(coinFlip == 1)
					{
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(1), 5);
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(1), 5);
					}
					else 
					{
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(2), 5);
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(2), 5);
					};	
				};
			
				if(this.$SIRF_shipRole = "escort")
					this.ship.switchAI("oolite-escortAI.js");
				else
				{
					this.ship.switchAI("oolite-shuttleAI.js");
				};	
				
				this.ship.primaryRole = "shuttle";
				break;

			case "SIRF_shuttle_system_neutral":
			case "SIRF_shuttle_system_neutral_team_01":

				this.ship.setCargoType("PLENTIFUL_GOODS");
				this.ship.switchAI("oolite-shuttleAI.js");
				this.ship.primaryRole = "shuttle";
				break;

			case "SIRF_worm_prospector":
				
				this.ship.switchAI("oolite-scavengerAI.js");
				break;
			
			case "SIRF_worm_prospector_miner":
			
				this.ship.switchAI("minerAI.plist");
				this.ship.primaryRole = "miner";
				break;
			
			case "SIRF_gecko_dragon_ssg":
			case "SIRF_gecko_dragon_ssg_team_01":
						
				if(this.ship.cargoSpaceUsed <= 1)
				{
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_space_jockeyCargo(), 1);
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_space_jockeyCargo(), 1);
				};
				
				if(this.$SIRF_shipType == "SIRF_gecko_dragon_ssg_team_01")
				{
					this.ship.switchAI("oolite-bountyHunterAI.js");
					this.ship.primaryRole = "hunter";
				};
				break;

			default: 
				break;		
		};	
	};
};

// resets accidental bounties caused by the model

this.shipAttackedOther = function(other)
{
    if(this.$SIRF_shipRole == "SIRF-YARD" && this.ship.bounty > 0)
	{
		if(ship && ship.isValid)
		{
			this.ship.bounty = 0;
			this.ship.setBounty(0, "friendly fire");
		};
	};		
};

this.shipBeingAttackedUnsuccessfully = function(whom)
{
	if((this.$SIRF_shipRole == "SIRF-YARD" || this.$SIRF_shipRole == "defense_ship") && this.ship.bounty > 0)
	{	
		if(whom && whom.isValid && ship && ship.isValid)
		{
			whom.target = null;
			whom.reactToAIMessage("TARGET_LOST");
			whom.removeDefenseTarget(this.ship);

			this.ship.target = null;
			this.ship.reactToAIMessage("TARGET_LOST");
			this.ship.removeDefenseTarget(whom);

			this.ship.bounty = 0;
			this.ship.setBounty(0, "friendly fire");
		};
	};	
};

this.shipBeingAttacked = function(whom)
{
	if((this.$SIRF_shipRole == "SIRF-YARD" || this.$SIRF_shipRole == "defense_ship") && this.ship.bounty > 0)
	{	
		if(whom && whom.isValid && ship && ship.isValid)
		{
			whom.target = null;
			whom.reactToAIMessage("TARGET_LOST");
			whom.removeDefenseTarget(this.ship);

			this.ship.target = null;
			this.ship.reactToAIMessage("TARGET_LOST");
			this.ship.removeDefenseTarget(whom);

			this.ship.bounty = 0;
			this.ship.setBounty(0, "friendly fire");
		};
	};	
};

this.shipAttackedWithMissile = function(missile, whom)
{
    if((this.$SIRF_shipRole == "SIRF-YARD" || this.$SIRF_shipRole == "defense_ship") && this.ship.bounty > 0)
	{	
		if(whom && whom.isValid && ship && ship.isValid)
		{
			whom.target = null;
			whom.reactToAIMessage("TARGET_LOST");
			whom.removeDefenseTarget(this.ship);

			this.ship.target = null;
			this.ship.reactToAIMessage("TARGET_LOST");
			this.ship.removeDefenseTarget(whom);

			this.ship.bounty = 0;
			this.ship.setBounty(0, "friendly fire");
		};
	};
};

this.shipDied = function(whom, why)
{
	if(this.ship.hasRole("escape-capsule"))
	{
		return;
	}
	else
	{
		// neutral inits first
		var podType = "escape-capsule";
		var criminalCrew = 0;
		var debrisCount = 0;
		var cargoType = "";
		var cargoPod = "cargopod";
		var cargoLoad = this.ship.cargoSpaceUsed;
		var cargoCount = 0;
				
		if(this.ship.bounty > 7)
			criminalCrew = 1;
		
		switch(this.$SIRF_shipType) 
		{
			case "SIRF_gecko_dragon_ssg":
			case "SIRF_gecko_dragon_ssg_team_01":
						
				if(criminalCrew == 1)
					podType = "SIRF_escape_capsule_ssg_pirate";	
				else
				{
					podType = "SIRF_escape_capsule_ssg";
				};

				debrisCount = 1;	
				break;
						
			case "SIRF_shuttle_system":
			case "SIRF_shuttle_system_team_01":
				
				if(criminalCrew == 1)
					podType = "SIRF_escape_capsule_SIRF_pirate";	
				else
				{
					podType = "SIRF_escape_capsule_SIRF";
				};
				
				debrisCount = this.$getRndInteger(1, 2);	
				break;

			case "SIRF_shuttle_system_neutral":
			case "SIRF_shuttle_system_neutral_team_01":
						
				if(criminalCrew == 1)
					podType = "SIRF_escape_capsule_pirate";	
				else
				{
					podType = "SIRF_escape_capsule_neutral";
				};	
				
				debrisCount = this.$getRndInteger(1, 2);	
				break;

			case "SIRF_worm_prospector":
			case "SIRF_worm_prospector_miner":
				
				if(criminalCrew == 1)
					podType = "SIRF_escape_suit_SIRF_pirate";	
				else
				{
					podType = "SIRF_escape_suit_SIRF";
				};
				
				debrisCount = 1;

				// need to check here so that possible findings before come first
				if(cargoLoad == 0)
				{
					if(this.$SIRF_shipType == "SIRF_worm_prospector")
						this.ship.setCargoType("PLENTIFUL_GOODS");
					else
					{
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 2);
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 2);
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 2);
					};		
				};	
				break;
			
			case "SIRF_worm_prospector_neutral":

				if(criminalCrew == 1)
					podType = "SIRF_escape_suit_pirate";	
				else
				{
					podType = "SIRF_escape_suit_neutral";
				};
				
				debrisCount = 1;
			
				if(cargoLoad == 0)
				{
					if(this.$SIRF_shipRole == "miner")
					{
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 3);
						this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 3);
					}
					else
					{
						this.ship.setCargoType("PLENTIFUL_GOODS");
					};	
				};
				break;

			// a big explosion with a lot of action, plenty alloys from the core-game so just other debris added
			case "SIRFyard":
			case "SIRF_shipyard_01":
			case "SIRF_shipyard_02":
			case "SIRF_shipyard_03":

				if(cargoLoad == 0)
				{
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(2), 3);
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(2), 5);
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(1), 3);
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(1), 5);
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 3);
					this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 3);
				};	

				system.addShips("SIRF_shuttle_system", this.$getRndInteger(5, 10), this.ship.position);
				system.addShips("SIRF_worm_prospector_lifeboat", this.$getRndInteger(5, 10), this.ship.position);
				system.addShips("SIRF_escape_pod_SIRF", this.$getRndInteger(10, 15), this.ship.position);

				for(var i = this.ship.cargoList.length - 1 ; i >= 0 ; --i)
				{
					cargoType = this.ship.cargoList[i].commodity;
					cargoPod = ("MRP01_container_" + cargoType);
					cargoCount = this.ship.cargoList[i].quantity;
								
					system.addShips(cargoPod, cargoCount, this.ship.position);
				};
				
				system.addShips("MRP01_container_cash", this.$getRndInteger(2, 6), this.ship.position);
				system.addShips("MRP01_container_prisoners", this.$getRndInteger(2, 4), this.ship.position);

				system.addShips("MRP01_effects_explosive_shrapnel", this.$getRndInteger(20, 40), this.ship.position);	
				system.addShips("gold", this.$getRndInteger(8, 15), this.ship.position);
				system.addShips("platinum", this.$getRndInteger(8, 15), this.ship.position);
				system.addShips("radioactives", this.$getRndInteger(8, 15), this.ship.position);
				debrisCount = (this.ship.fuel.toFixed(0)) * 2;	
				system.addShips("MRP01_effects_burningFuel", debrisCount, this.ship.position);
				return;
			
			default: 
				break;
		};
		
		// debris for the larger subs
		if(this.ship.hasRole("SIRF_station_sub"))
		{
			this.ship.owner.commsMessage(this.ship.name + " hit, rescue teams move in.");
			
			if(cargoLoad == 0)
			{
				this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(2), 3);
				this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationCargo(1), 3);
				this.ship.adjustCargo(this.$SIRF_stationMining(), 3);
			};
			
			system.addShips("SIRF_escape_pod_SIRF", this.$getRndInteger(3, 5), this.ship.owner.position);

			for(var i = this.ship.cargoList.length - 1 ; i >= 0 ; --i)
			{
				cargoType = this.ship.cargoList[i].commodity;
				cargoPod = ("MRP01_container_" + cargoType);
				cargoCount = this.ship.cargoList[i].quantity;
							
				system.addShips(cargoPod, cargoCount, this.ship.owner.position);
				this.ship.owner.throwSpark();
			};
				
			system.addShips("MRP01_container_cash", this.$getRndInteger(1, 2), this.ship.owner.position);
			
			system.addShips("MRP01_effects_explosive_shrapnel", this.$getRndInteger(5, 10), this.ship.owner.position);	
			system.addShips("MRP01_ship_debris", this.$getRndInteger(5, 10), this.ship.owner.position);
			return;
		};
		
		// emergency crafts
		if(debrisCount > 0)
			system.addShips(podType, debrisCount, this.ship.position);

		// cargopods
		if(cargoLoad > 0)
		{
			for(var i = this.ship.cargoList.length - 1 ; i >= 0 ; --i)
			{
				cargoType = this.ship.cargoList[i].commodity;
				cargoPod = ("MRP01_container_" + cargoType);
				cargoCount = this.ship.cargoList[i].quantity;
							
				system.addShips(cargoPod, cargoCount, this.ship.position);
			};
		};
			
		/*
		// outsourced to Montanas Ressource Pack 01 V 0.54

		debrisCount = this.$getRndInteger(3, 6);
		// explosive shrapnels
		system.addShips("MRP01_effects_explosive_shrapnel", debrisCount, this.ship.position);
		// various depris
		system.addShips("MRP01_ship_debris", debrisCount, this.ship.position);
		// burning fuel
		debrisCount = (this.ship.fuel.toFixed(0));	
		system.addShips("MRP01_effects_burningFuel", debrisCount, this.ship.position);
		*/
	};
};

this.$SIRF_stationCargo = function(flip)
{
	// SIRF main imports (market script)
	this.$SIRF_station_cargo_in_array = ["food", "radioactives", "slaves", "furs"];
	var station_cargo_in = 
	$SIRF_station_cargo_in_array[Math.floor(Math.random() * $SIRF_station_cargo_in_array.length)];
	
	// SIRF main exports (market script)
	this.$SIRF_station_cargo_out_array = ["computers", "machinery", "alloys", "firearms"];
	var station_cargo_out = 
	$SIRF_station_cargo_out_array[Math.floor(Math.random() * $SIRF_station_cargo_out_array.length)];

	if(flip == 1)
		station_cargo = station_cargo_in;
	else
	{
		station_cargo = station_cargo_out;	
	};
	
	return (station_cargo);
};

this.$SIRF_stationMining = function()
{
	this.$SIRF_station_miner_array = ["alloys", "minerals", "gold", "platinum", "gem_stones"];
	var station_miner = 
	$SIRF_station_miner_array[Math.floor(Math.random() * $SIRF_station_miner_array.length)];
		
	return (station_miner);
};

// food, booze and guns, what else you need for your trip ? :P
this.$SIRF_space_jockeyCargo = function()
{
	this.$SIRF_space_jockey_cargo_array = ["firearms", "food", "liquor_wines"];

	if(worldScripts["witchfire-populator"])  // Darkside Moonshine Distillery OXP
		this.$SIRF_space_jockey_cargo_array.push("witchfire_whiskey");

	var space_jockey_cargo = 
	$SIRF_space_jockey_cargo_array[Math.floor(Math.random() * $SIRF_space_jockey_cargo_array.length)];

	return (space_jockey_cargo);
};

this.$getRndInteger = function(min, max)
{
	return Math.floor(Math.random() * (max - min + 1) ) + min;
};

    this.name			= "SIRF_ships_spawn_conditions";
this.author			= "Montana05";
this.description	= "Conditions for the spawn of some SIRF ships";
this.version		= "2.62";
this.copyright		= "2021 Montana05";
this.licence   		= "CC BY-NC-SA 4.0";
"use strict";

this.allowSpawnShip = function(shipKey) 
{
	if(system.isInterstellarSpace || system.sun.isGoingNova || system.sun.hasGoneNova || 
	   system.government < 3 || system.techLevel < 7 || system.techLevel > 13 || 
	   system.countShipsWithRole("SIRF-YARD") < 1)
	{
		return false;
	}
	else return true;
};
    Scripts/SIRF_station_selection_conditions.js 
    this.name			= "SIRF_station_selection_conditions";
this.author			= "Montana05";
this.description	= "Conditions for SIRF tech levels and price factors";
this.version		= "2.62";
this.copyright		= "2021 Montana05";
this.licence   		= "CC BY-NC-SA 4.0";
"use strict";

this.allowSpawnShip = function(shipKey) 
{
	var systemTech = system.techLevel;
	var systemEco = system.economy;
	var systemGov = system.government;
	
	if(system.isInterstellarSpace || system.sun.isGoingNova || system.sun.hasGoneNova || 
		systemGov < 3 || systemTech < 7 || systemTech > 13)
	{
		return false;
	}
		
	switch(shipKey) 
	{
		case "SIRF_shipyard_01":	
			
			if(systemTech == 7 || systemTech == 8)
			{
				log(this.name, "SIRF added to the system, tech level = 9, price factor = 1.10");
				return true;
			}
			break;
			
		case "SIRF_shipyard_02":	
			
			if(systemTech == 9 || systemTech == 10)
			{
				log(this.name, "SIRF added to the system, tech level = 11, price factor = 1.15");
				return true;
			}
			break;
			
		case "SIRF_shipyard_03":	
			
			if(systemTech == 11 || (systemTech == 12 && systemEco != 0))
			{
				log(this.name, "SIRF added to the system, tech level = 13, price factor = 1.20");
				return true;
			}
			break;
			
		case "SIRFyard":	
			
			if((systemTech == 12 && systemEco == 0) || systemTech == 13)
			{
				log(this.name, "SIRF added to the system, tech level = 15, price factor = 1.25");
				return true;
			}
			break;
			
		default:
			break;		
	};
	return false;	
};
